@startuml CompleteSystemArchitecture
!theme plain
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam defaultFontSize 10
skinparam roundcorner 6

' === HEADER ===
title HỆ THỐNG GIÁM SÁT CHẤT LƯỢNG KHÔNG KHÍ - KIẾN TRÚC TỔNG THỂ

' === LAYER 1: DEVICES ===
package "Layer 1: Thiết bị đo" <<device>> #LightBlue {
  [ESP32 Sensor Node] as ESP32
  [PMS5003\nPM1.0/PM2.5/PM10] as PMS
  [DHT22\nTemp/Humidity] as DHT
  [JSON Payload\n{device_id, pm1, pm25...}] as JSON
}

ESP32 --> PMS : Serial
ESP32 --> DHT : Serial
PMS --> JSON : Format
DHT --> JSON : Format

' === LAYER 2: TRANSMISSION ===
package "Layer 2: Truyền dữ liệu" <<transmission>> #LightGreen {
  [MQTT Broker\nMosquitto:1883] as MQTT
  [Telegraf\nMQTT Consumer] as TELE
  [InfluxDB Cloud\nsensor_data] as INFLUX
}

ESP32 --> MQTT : MQTT
MQTT --> TELE : Subscribe
TELE --> INFLUX : Line Protocol

note bottom of INFLUX
**Tags:** sensor_node, location, host
**Fields:** pm1, pm25, pm10, temp, humidity, aqi
end note

' === LAYER 3: BACKEND ===
package "Layer 3: Backend Go:8088" <<backend>> #LightYellow {
  [RealtimePoller\n30s interval] as POLLER
  [WebSocketService] as WS
  [InfluxService] as INF_SVC

  database "PostgreSQL" as PG {
    [users]
    [sensors]
    [alerts]
    [settings]
    [sessions]
    [sensor_access]
  }

  [AlertService] as ALERT
  [MLService] as ML_CLI

  [REST API\n/v1/*] as REST
}

INFLUX --> INF_SVC : Query API
INF_SVC --> POLLER : Latest data
POLLER --> WS : Broadcast
POLLER --> ALERT : Check threshold
ALERT --> PG : Save alerts
INF_SVC --> REST : Query handlers
ML_CLI --> REST : Forecast handlers

' === LAYER 4: ML ===
package "Layer 4: ML Python:8000" <<ml>> #LightPink {
  [FastAPI Server] as FAST
  [LSTM] as LSTM
  [GRU] as GRU
  [BiLSTM] as BILSTM
  [Informer] as INF
  [ARIMA] as ARIMA

  [Drift Monitor\nPSI ≥ 5.0/10.0] as DRIFT
}

ML_CLI ..> FAST : POST /forecast
FAST --> LSTM : predict
FAST --> GRU : predict
FAST --> BILSTM : predict
FAST --> INF : predict
FAST --> ARIMA : predict

LSTM ..> DRIFT : monitor
GRU ..> DRIFT : monitor
BILSTM ..> DRIFT : monitor
INF ..> DRIFT : monitor

' === LAYER 5: FRONTEND ===
package "Layer 5: Frontend React:5173" <<frontend>> #LightCyan {
  [useWebSocket] as WS_HOOK
  [useApi\n(React Query)] as API_HOOK

  [Dashboard\nIndex.tsx] as DASH

  [KpiCard x6] as KPI
  [PMChart] as CHART
  [AqiGauge] as GAUGE
  [Heatmap] as HEAT
  [ForecastTable] as FTABLE
  [DriftTracking] as DTRACK

  [Pages:\nLocations, Alerts\nSettings, Reports] as PAGES
}

WS_HOOK --> DASH : realtime
API_HOOK --> DASH : REST
DASH --> KPI : display
DASH --> CHART : display
DASH --> GAUGE : display
DASH --> HEAT : display
DASH --> FTABLE : display
DASH --> DTRACK : display
DASH --> PAGES : nav

' === CONNECTIONS ===
REST -up-> WS_HOOK : WSS :8088
REST -up-> API_HOOK : HTTPS :8088
ML_CLI -up-> FAST : HTTP :8000

' === LEGEND ===
legend bottom right
  |= Color |= Layer |
  | <back:#LightBlue>   </back> | Thiết bị đo |
  | <back:#LightGreen>  </back> | Truyền dữ liệu |
  | <back:#LightYellow> </back> | Backend Go |
  | <back:#LightPink>   </back> | ML Service |
  | <back:#LightCyan>   </back> | Frontend React |
end legend

@enduml